{"tid":2508826,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夏博義改口 稱香港國安法合法及必須","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T04:32:28.000Z","uid":283837,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c719d337b264fb2769da184bfd852c92f1fb0190","tid":2508826,"uid":283837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"香港大律師公會主席夏博義昨日接受港媒訪問時透露，已退出英國自由民主黨，強調自己並非政客亦不「反華」。對於就任大律師公會主席後曾指責香港國安法不符合法治精神，夏博義指自己一直認為香港國安法屬合法及必須，大多數國家都有訂立維護國家安全的法例，但又對個別條文有意見，日後會向政府提交建議書。<br />\n<br />\n　　中聯辦發言人早前曾痛斥夏博義是「反華政客」，為違法者張目。夏博義老調重彈辯解道，大律師公會並非政治組織，只是一群捍衛法治的大律師，認為外界甚至中聯辦誤解公會。<br />\n<br />\n　　夏博義的上述立場轉變，或許有近期社會各界強烈不滿其反華仇中論調，要求其辭去大律師公會主席有關，對於夏博義的改口說詞，相信各界拭目以待，會繼續聽其言觀其行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2021/0429/580009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fhongkong%2Ftext%2F2021%2F0429%2F580009.html&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=5e51a553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2021/0429/580009.html</a>"},{"pid":"43cbf823935a9665872a7ddc20738dc1303777f2","tid":2508826,"uid":281189,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"終於都跪咗<br />\n香港就係咁撚樣沉淪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c3e19bb68688690bef438fc393c185756a0e0f","tid":2508826,"uid":47042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:17:29.000Z","msg":"佢不嬲都係話對個別條文有意見架啦"},{"pid":"ac2fa74fcf992c8804cc14a75d9a26c05132354e","tid":2508826,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2508153/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2508153/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cl